  "browser_support": "All modern browsers.",
  "performance_notes": "The burst is a set of pre-placed particles animated once via a toggled class; the heart scales with a keyframe. No per-frame JS.",
  "accessibility_notes": "It's a real <button> with aria-pressed reflecting liked state and an accessible label that updates (Like/Unlike). Burst is decorative (aria-hidden) and skipped under prefers-reduced-motion.",
